front.title: •Colonel Wullf Yularen
front.gametext: Power +1 if at the same site with Tarkin, Chief Bast or General Dodonna.
front.lore: Imperial Security Bureau (ISB) officer assigned to brief Tarkin. Also ordered to ensure absolute loyalty to the Emperor. Leader. Will stop at nothing to fulfill the Emperor's will.

rulings: Only gains power +1 even if with multiple characters listed.
